Class Coffee

java.lang.Object

com.example.project4.Coffee
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Coffee extends MenuItem implements Customizable
Class for creating a coffee order and storing the order in an ArrayList. Object will store size, addins, and total cost.
Author:
Sebastian Carrasco, Rachael Chin
